OL,3,CTony Morley reflects on 1982 Villa
OL,4,Cglory ahead of Europe tie in
OL,5,Cdocumentary
OL,7,FAston Villa legend Tony Morley has
OL,8,Ftold ITV News Central "the European
OL,9,FCup is a fairytale," as he admits he
OL,10,Fwill be thinking of former teammates.
OL,12,FSpeaking to Sports Correspondent Dan
OL,13,FSalisbury-Jones on Aston Villa:
OL,14,FRoaring Again he says returning to a
OL,15,FEuropean stage brings back powerful
OL,16,Femotions from the club's 1982 triumph.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
