PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779307554
OL,3,CTony Morley reflects on 1982 Villa
OL,4,Cglory ahead of Europe tie in
OL,5,Cdocumentary
OL,7,FMorley was part of the side that
OL,8,Fhelped Aston Villa become champions of
OL,9,FEurope in 1982, setting up Peter
OL,10,FWithe's winner in the final against
OL,11,FBayern Munich - a moment still etched
OL,12,Finto football history more than four
OL,13,Fdecades on.
OL,15,FAs Villa prepare for another defining
OL,16,FEuropean night, Morley reflects on
OL,17,Fwhat the occasion means, not just in
OL,18,Fterms of footballing achievement, but
OL,19,Fpersonal memory, friendship, and loss.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779307554
OL,3,CTony Morley reflects on 1982 Villa
OL,4,Cglory ahead of Europe tie in
OL,5,Cdocumentary
OL,7,F"It'll fetch memories... I'll be
OL,8,Fthinking of them, definitely," he
OL,9,Fsaid, before adding: "I'd love for
OL,10,Fthem to be with us... you want to be
OL,11,Fout there, you want to be a part of
OL,12,Fit."
OL,14,FHe also recalls the surreal journey
OL,15,Ffrom playing grassroots football to
OL,16,Fthe biggest stage in club football.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779307554
OL,3,CTony Morley reflects on 1982 Villa
OL,4,Cglory ahead of Europe tie in
OL,5,Cdocumentary
OL,7,FHe told ITV News: "You go back and you
OL,8,Fthink this is surreal... all of a
OL,9,Fsudden you're playing one of the
OL,10,Fbiggest competitions in the world. For
OL,11,Fme it is a privilege."
OL,13,FMorley's reflections form part of ITV
OL,14,FNews Central's wider coverage of
OL,15,FVilla's European resurgence, featured
OL,16,Fin the new ITVX documentary Aston
OL,17,FVilla: Roaring Again, presented by
OL,18,FSports Correspondent Dan Salisbury-
OL,19,FJones.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
