FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779307554
OL,3,CTony Morley reflects on 1982 Villa
OL,4,Cglory ahead of Europe tie in
OL,5,Cdocumentary
OL,7,FThe documentary reflects the club's
OL,8,Fjourney from its historic 1982 triumph
OL,9,Fthrough decades of change, hardship
OL,10,Fand revival - and into a modern era
OL,11,Fwhere European nights at Villa Park
OL,12,Fhave returned under manager Unai Emery.
OL,14,FIt also revisits key turning points in
OL,15,Fthe club's recent history, from
OL,16,Frelegation battles and ownership
OL,17,Fchange, to the return of belief and
OL,18,Fambition that has restored Villa among
OL,19,FEurope's contenders.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779307554
OL,3,CTony Morley reflects on 1982 Villa
OL,4,Cglory ahead of Europe tie in
OL,5,Cdocumentary
OL,7,FFor Morley, however, the emotion
OL,8,Fremains rooted in the past, and the
OL,9,Fpeople who made it unforgettable.
OL,11,F"We'd be the ones at the bar, having a
OL,12,Ffew drinks, having a laugh," he said,
OL,13,Freflecting on former teammates
OL,14,Fincluding Gary Shaw.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, they can't be here...
OL,17,FI'll be thinking of them, definitely."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
